title: Naruto And The Rest Of Team 7 Arrive On The Fortnite Island
author: Fortnite
description:
Naruto Uzumaki, the Jinchūriki host of the all-powerful nine-tailed beast is coming to the Island along with the rest of Team 7 with Sasuke Uchiha, Sakura Haruno, and Kakashi Hatake. https://fn.gg/Naruto

Play Fortnite Battle Royale, the completely free 100-player PvP mode. One giant map, A Battle Bus, Last one standing wins. ESRB Rating: Teen with Violence.
